fields.name: Code
fields.description: An identifier for the error. Codes are invariant and are intended to be consumed programmatically.

fields.name: Details
fields.description: A list of additional details about the error.

fields.name: Message
fields.description: A message describing the error, intended to be suitable for display in a user interface.

fields.name: Target
fields.description: The target of the particular error. For example, the name of the property in error.
